teacherInfo.bio:
We are an elite group of scholars of language and religion who graduated from al-Azhar University (pioneer center of Islamic and Arabic learning in the world). We have created an online school to share our knowledge with you. We do not belong to any sect or specific Islamic trend. Our team includes experienced instructors who teach a wide variety of subjects ranging from Arabic language to Quranic recitation, fiqh and tafsir. We are happy to meet with you to establish your learning needs and design a course that will meet them.
Since Allah’s Quranic revelation began with the word ‘iqra’ which means ‘read,’ we seek to please Allah (swt) by teaching his book and sharing the traditions of the prophet (pbh) as we learned them. Our prophet Mohamed (pbuh) said that the best among you are those who learn the Quran and teach it. Our teachers adhere to the highest ethical standards and your feedback is always welcomed by Waraqa.
